org.wicketstuff.jslibraries

Interface Provider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CDN, LocalProvider

    public interface Provider
    A Provider is an optional means of overriding the HeaderContributor created by JSLib.
    If you use JSLib.getHeaderContributor(versionDescriptor, provider[]) , these providers get the opportunity to provide a HeaderContributor first. If it returns null, the requested lib will be served from the application instead (if defined).
